<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="mercy-n">mercy <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mɜːsi/    美 /'mɜːrsi/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>仁慈；怜悯；宽恕：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>have mercy on</strong>
对…表示怜悯</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>showed little mercy to</strong> the prisoners. 
他们对囚犯毫不留情。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-the-mercy-of">at the mercy of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>完全受…支配；任凭…摆布：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The little ship was at the mercy of the storm. 
小船在暴风雨中失去控制。</p></div></div>